Format 60

Columns			1
Sides			1
DefaultStyle		Standard


ClassOptions
	FontSize             12
	PageStyle            empty|head|foot|headandfoot
End

Input article.layout

Input stdtitle.inc
Input stdlists.inc
Input stdinsets.inc
Input stdfloats.inc
Input stdcustom.inc
Input stdcounters.inc

NoStyle Subsubsection
NoStyle Subsubsection*
NoStyle Paragraph
NoStyle Subparagraph
NoStyle Paragraph*
NoStyle Subparagraph*
NoStyle Abstract
NoStyle Quote
NoStyle Verse
NoStyle Bibliography
#NoStyle Itemize
NoStyle Address
NoStyle Right_Address

Counter answersCounter
End

#### Question styles

Style SmartQuestion
  CopyStyle	Enumerate
  Category	Questions
  LatexType        Item_Environment
  LatexName       myquestions
  ItemCommand	myquestion
  LabelType	Enumerate
  LabelSep	xx
  ResetArgs	1

  Argument 	item:1
    MenuString	"Point Value"
    Tooltip	"Specify the value for the points of this question. Use CTRL-L \half for 0.5 points."
    LabelString	"Points"
  EndArgument
End

########## support for \fillin is with insets
InsetLayout "Flex:Fill in (blank)"
  LyxType	Custom
  LatexType	Command
  LatexName	fillin
  KeepEmpty	1   # don't want anything in the inset
  LabelString	"_________ (fill in blank)" 
  Argument 1
    MenuString     "Answer"
    Tooltip           "Specify the answer (only appears when printing the answers)"
    LabelString    "Answer"
    AutoInsert	1
  EndArgument
  Argument 2
    MenuString     "Width"
    Tooltip           "Specify the value for the width of the blank, e.g. 2in"
    LabelString    "Width"    
  EndArgument
End


